annotations.description: Create something more natural than Nature. Bring Nature to your everyday life. The Nature Aquarium is a proposal to construct your own piece of Nature with all its beauty, as a part of the interior design of your home. Simplicity and Clarity are the two key factors we paid close attention to in designing aquarium tanks for The Nature Aquarium. Eliminating plastic frames and refining the use of silicon as not to clash the clarity of the glass made of selected material. The Nature Aquarium concept has succeeded to design glass aquarium tanks which give your aquascapes a boundless panorama.           Specifications for 60-H (45) High Clarity Glass:     Hand made by specialized craftsmen with high quality glass and highly durable silicon.  2 year quality warranty  8 stainless steel hooks included for placing glass cover on Cube Garden  Dimension: 60x45x45cm (approx:24"x18"x18")  Glass thickness: 8mm  Volume: 32 Gallons
annotations.title: ADA Cube Garden 60-H (45) Aquarium (Ultra High Clarity Glass)
